PowerShell Commands:
------------------------------------------
Check Node & npm:
1. node -v
2. npm -v
------------------------------------------
Install Chocolatey:
Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force
------------------------------------------
Install Node.js (LTS):
choco install nodejs-lts -y
------------------------------------------
Check Git:
git --version
------------------------------------------
Clone OWASP Juice Shop:
1. git clone https://github.com/juice-shop/juice-shop.git
2. cd juice-shop
------------------------------------------
Install Application Dependencies:
npm install
------------------------------------------
Start the Application:
npm start
------------------------------------------
Target URL (Browser):
http://localhost:3000
------------------------------------------
XSS Test Payload:
<script>alert('XSS');</script>
------------------------------------------
SQL Injection Test Payload:
admin' OR '1'='1
------------------------------------------
